- **Graduate/Year 1**: \$70,000-\$85,000 base + 10-30% bonus
- **Year 2-3**: \$85,000-\$110,000 base + 10-30% bonus
- **Year 4-6 (Senior Analyst)**: \$110,000-\$150,000 base + 30-60% bonus
